Example app of how to fill a plan with routines and steps.

To install:

*Make sure you have rvm and the bundler gem in 1.9.2@global gemset*

git clone git://github.com/sinfante/plan_app.git
cd plan_app
bundle install
cp config/database.yml.example config/database.yml

*Edit the database.yml file with your database info*

rake db:create
rake db:migrate
rails server

*go to localhost:3000/plans in your favorite browser*
